```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_returns.sql
-- Deduplicate returns to one approved return per item (earliest approved)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY CASE WHEN status = 'approved' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ASC,
                     return_date ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    return_id,
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
    AND status = 'approved'
```

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_order_items_with_returns.sql
-- Join order items with deduped returns to track which items were returned
WITH items AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.order_id,
        oi.product_id,
        oi.quantity,
        oi.unit_price
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
)
SELECT
    i.item_id,
    i.order_id,
    i.product_id,
    i.quantity,
    i.unit_price,
    CASE WHEN r.return_id IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS is_returned
FROM items i
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} r
    ON r.item_id = i.item_id
```

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_items_with_products.sql
-- Join items with products and categories
WITH items_returns AS (
    SELECT
        iir.item_id,
        iir.product_id,
        iir.quantity,
        iir.is_returned
    FROM {{ ref('int_order_items_with_returns') }} iir
)
SELECT
    ir.item_id,
    ir.product_id,
    COALESCE(p.category_id, -1) AS category_id,
    ir.quantity,
    ir.is_returned
FROM items_returns ir
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
    ON p.product_id = ir.product_id
```

-- models/mart/fct_return_rate_by_category.sql
-- Calculate return rates by category
WITH items_with_categories AS (
    SELECT
        iwp.item_id,
        iwp.category_id,
        iwp.is_returned
    FROM {{ ref('int_items_with_products') }} iwp
)
SELECT
    COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name,
    COUNT(iwc.item_id) AS total_items_sold,
    SUM(iwc.is_returned) AS total_items_returned,
    ROUND(
        SUM(iwc.is_returned)::NUMERIC / COUNT(iwc.item_id),
        4
    ) AS return_rate
FROM items_with_categories iwc
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
    ON c.category_id = iwc.category_id
GROUP BY
    COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)')
ORDER BY return_rate DESC
